data.description: Welcome to your cozy haven of convenience! Nestled near Highway 90 and Sam Houston Tollway, this single-story gem invites you into a world of seamless connections and comfort. The living room flows into a charming formal dining space, perfect for gatherings. The split formal dining room connects to a well-appointed kitchen, making hosting a breeze. An extra air-conditioned room adds versatility, with utility space and a closet area. Outside, find a shed with electrical hookups ready to transform into your creative workspace. Enjoy the comfort and efficiency of the new AC unit and water softener from 2021. Join the vibrant community with a pool and nearby park. Conveniently close to restaurants and amenities, this home offers a perfect blend of practicality and leisure. Your cozy retreat awaits—schedule your visit and step into the next exciting chapter of your life!
